#: index.docbook:46
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&umbrello; helps the software development process by using the industry "
"standard Unified Modelling Language (&UML;) to enable you to create diagrams "
"for designing and documenting your systems."
msgstr ""
"&umbrello; helpt bij het softwareontwikkelingsproces door gebruikmaking van "
"de industrie standaard Unified Modelling Language (&UML;). opdat u "
"diagrammen kunt maken om uw systeem te ontwerpen en te documenteren."

